// model by eon/sketchfab https://sketchfab.com/3d-models/elven-ranger-statue-71aec2d9f7724ae09992435ce8ff7258

import './fix'
import * as THREE from 'three'
import { render } from 'react-dom'
import React, { Suspense, useEffect, useRef, useMemo } from 'react'
import { Canvas, useThree, useFrame, useLoader, extend } from 'react-three-fiber'
import { EffectComposer } from 'three/examples/jsm/postprocessing/EffectComposer'
import { RenderPass } from 'three/examples/jsm/postprocessing/RenderPass'
import { ShaderPass } from 'three/examples/jsm/postprocessing/ShaderPass'
import { FXAAShader } from 'three/examples/jsm/shaders/FXAAShader'
import { GLTFLoader } from 'three/examples/jsm/loaders/GLTFLoader'
import { DRACOLoader } from 'three/examples/jsm/loaders/DRACOLoader'
import { AdditiveBlendingShader, VolumetricLightShader } from './shaders'
import './styles.css'

extend({ EffectComposer, RenderPass, ShaderPass })

const DEFAULT_LAYER = 0
const OCCLUSION_LAYER = 1

// Component auto-generated by GLTFJSX: https://github.com/react-spring/gltfjsx
function Elf(props) {
    const group = useRef()
    const { nodes, materials } = useLoader(GLTFLoader, '/bugatti.glb')
    return (
        <group ref={group} {...props} dispose={null}>
            <mesh
                material={materials['Studio_Lights.005']}
                geometry={nodes.alights014_Plane051.geometry}
                rotation={[Math.PI / 2, 0, 0]}
            />
            <mesh
                material={materials['Studio_Lights.005']}
                geometry={nodes.alights000_Plane049.geometry}
                rotation={[Math.PI / 2, 0, 0]}
            />
            <mesh
                material={materials['Studio_Lights.005']}
                geometry={nodes.alights015_Plane050.geometry}
                rotation={[Math.PI / 2, 0, 0]}
            />
            <mesh material={materials.sun} geometry={nodes.Plane047_Plane042.geometry} rotation={[Math.PI / 2, 0, 0]} />
            <mesh material={materials.sun} geometry={nodes.Plane036_Plane040.geometry} rotation={[Math.PI / 2, 0, 0]} />
            <mesh
                material={materials['silver_door_strip.004']}
                geometry={nodes.Cube028_Cube030.geometry}
                rotation={[Math.PI / 2, 0, 0]}
            />
            <mesh
                material={materials['silver_door_strip.004']}
                geometry={nodes.Cube027_Cube025.geometry}
                rotation={[Math.PI / 2, 0, 0]}
            />
            <mesh
                material={materials['silver_door_strip.004']}
                geometry={nodes.Plane026.geometry}
                rotation={[Math.PI / 2, 0, 0]}
            />
            <mesh material={materials.breaks_} geometry={nodes.Cube029_Cube031.geometry} rotation={[Math.PI / 2, 0, 0]} />
            <mesh material={materials.breaks_} geometry={nodes.Icosphere.geometry} rotation={[Math.PI / 2, 0, 0]} />
            <mesh material={materials.red_glass} geometry={nodes.Icosphere001.geometry} rotation={[Math.PI / 2, 0, 0]} />
            <mesh material={materials.None} geometry={nodes.Plane013_Plane014.geometry} rotation={[Math.PI / 2, 0, 0]} />
            <mesh material={materials.None} geometry={nodes.Cube038.geometry} rotation={[Math.PI / 2, 0, 0]} />
            <group rotation={[Math.PI / 2, 0, 0]}>
                <mesh material={materials['tyre.004']} geometry={nodes['Cube.048_Cube.080_0'].geometry} />
                <mesh material={materials['rim_silver.004']} geometry={nodes['Cube.048_Cube.080_1'].geometry} />
                <mesh material={materials['rim_blue.004']} geometry={nodes['Cube.048_Cube.080_2'].geometry} />
                <mesh material={materials['Nut.004']} geometry={nodes['Cube.048_Cube.080_3'].geometry} />
                <mesh material={materials['brake_disk.004']} geometry={nodes['Cube.048_Cube.080_4'].geometry} />
                <mesh material={materials['wheel_joint.004']} geometry={nodes['Cube.048_Cube.080_5'].geometry} />
                <mesh material={materials['cALLIPERS.004']} geometry={nodes['Cube.048_Cube.080_6'].geometry} />
                <mesh material={materials['silver_door_strip.004']} geometry={nodes['Cube.048_Cube.080_7'].geometry} />
            </group>
            <group rotation={[Math.PI / 2, 0, 0]}>
                <mesh material={materials['tyre.004']} geometry={nodes['Cube.046_Cube.063_0'].geometry} />
                <mesh material={materials['rim_silver.004']} geometry={nodes['Cube.046_Cube.063_1'].geometry} />
                <mesh material={materials['rim_blue.004']} geometry={nodes['Cube.046_Cube.063_2'].geometry} />
                <mesh material={materials['Nut.004']} geometry={nodes['Cube.046_Cube.063_3'].geometry} />
                <mesh material={materials['brake_disk.004']} geometry={nodes['Cube.046_Cube.063_4'].geometry} />
                <mesh material={materials['wheel_joint.004']} geometry={nodes['Cube.046_Cube.063_5'].geometry} />
                <mesh material={materials['cALLIPERS.004']} geometry={nodes['Cube.046_Cube.063_6'].geometry} />
                <mesh material={materials['silver_door_strip.004']} geometry={nodes['Cube.046_Cube.063_7'].geometry} />
            </group>
            <group rotation={[Math.PI / 2, 0, 0]}>
                <mesh material={materials['tyre.004']} geometry={nodes['Cube.039_0'].geometry} />
                <mesh material={materials['rim_silver.004']} geometry={nodes['Cube.039_1'].geometry} />
                <mesh material={materials['rim_blue.004']} geometry={nodes['Cube.039_2'].geometry} />
                <mesh material={materials['Nut.004']} geometry={nodes['Cube.039_3'].geometry} />
                <mesh material={materials['brake_disk.004']} geometry={nodes['Cube.039_4'].geometry} />
                <mesh material={materials['wheel_joint.004']} geometry={nodes['Cube.039_5'].geometry} />
                <mesh material={materials['cALLIPERS.004']} geometry={nodes['Cube.039_6'].geometry} />
                <mesh material={materials['silver_door_strip.004']} geometry={nodes['Cube.039_7'].geometry} />
            </group>
            <mesh
                material={materials['WHITE.002']}
                geometry={nodes.Text001_Text002.geometry}
                rotation={[Math.PI / 2, 0, 0]}
            />
            <mesh
                material={materials['WHITE.002']}
                geometry={nodes.Text002_Text001.geometry}
                rotation={[Math.PI / 2, 0, 0]}
            />
            <group rotation={[Math.PI / 2, 0, 0]}>
                <mesh material={materials['red.002']} geometry={nodes['Cylinder.026_Cylinder.025_0'].geometry} />
                <mesh material={materials['silver_door_strip.004']} geometry={nodes['Cylinder.026_Cylinder.025_1'].geometry} />
            </group>
            <mesh
                material={materials['Studio_Lights.004']}
                geometry={nodes.Plane024.geometry}
                rotation={[Math.PI / 2, 0, 0]}
            />
            <mesh material={materials['GRILL.004']} geometry={nodes.Cube036.geometry} rotation={[Math.PI / 2, 0, 0]} />
            <mesh
                material={materials['GRILL.004']}
                geometry={nodes.Cube043_Cube081.geometry}
                rotation={[Math.PI / 2, 0, 0]}
            />
            <mesh material={materials['GRILL.004']} geometry={nodes.Cube044.geometry} rotation={[Math.PI / 2, 0, 0]} />
            <mesh
                material={materials['back_drop.004']}
                geometry={nodes.Cylinder027_Cylinder026.geometry}
                rotation={[Math.PI / 2, 0, 0]}
            />
            <group rotation={[Math.PI / 2, 0, 0]}>
                <mesh material={materials.red_glass} geometry={nodes['Plane.014_Plane.020_0'].geometry} />
                <mesh material={materials.silver_trim} geometry={nodes['Plane.014_Plane.020_1'].geometry} />
            </group>
            <mesh material={materials.black_cable} geometry={nodes.BezierCurve.geometry} rotation={[Math.PI / 2, 0, 0]} />
            <mesh material={materials.ENGINE} geometry={nodes.Cube026_Cube020.geometry} rotation={[Math.PI / 2, 0, 0]} />
            <mesh
                material={materials.NAVY}
                geometry={nodes.Cylinder034_Cylinder131.geometry}
                rotation={[Math.PI / 2, 0, 0]}
            />
            <group rotation={[Math.PI / 2, 0, 0]}>
                <mesh material={materials.aluminiumm} geometry={nodes['Cylinder.033_Cylinder.126_0'].geometry} />
                <mesh material={materials.glossy} geometry={nodes['Cylinder.033_Cylinder.126_1'].geometry} />
                <mesh material={materials.white_holders} geometry={nodes['Cylinder.033_Cylinder.126_2'].geometry} />
            </group>
            <group rotation={[Math.PI / 2, 0, 0]}>
                <mesh material={materials['headlight_glass.004']} geometry={nodes['Cube.042_0'].geometry} />
                <mesh material={materials['headlight_square.004']} geometry={nodes['Cube.042_1'].geometry} />
            </group>
            <group rotation={[Math.PI / 2, 0, 0]}>
                <mesh material={materials['reflective_coat.004']} geometry={nodes['Plane.027_0'].geometry} />
                <mesh material={materials['glass_front.004']} geometry={nodes['Plane.027_1'].geometry} />
                <mesh material={materials['Trim.004']} geometry={nodes['Plane.027_2'].geometry} />
            </group>
            <group rotation={[Math.PI / 2, 0, 0]}>
                <mesh material={materials['BLUE.002']} geometry={nodes['Plane.028_0'].geometry} />
                <mesh material={materials['silver_door_strip.004']} geometry={nodes['Plane.028_1'].geometry} />
                <mesh material={materials.NAVY} geometry={nodes['Plane.028_2'].geometry} />
                <mesh material={materials['front_window.004']} geometry={nodes['Plane.028_3'].geometry} />
                <mesh material={materials['black_fuel_tank.004']} geometry={nodes['Plane.028_4'].geometry} />
                <mesh material={materials['black_strip.004']} geometry={nodes['Plane.028_5'].geometry} />
                <mesh material={materials['WHEEL_CURB.004']} geometry={nodes['Plane.028_6'].geometry} />
                <mesh material={materials['black_vent.004']} geometry={nodes['Plane.028_7'].geometry} />
                <mesh material={materials.black_side_vent} geometry={nodes['Plane.028_8'].geometry} />
                <mesh material={materials.Mirrors} geometry={nodes['Plane.028_9'].geometry} />
                <mesh material={materials.exhaust} geometry={nodes['Plane.028_10'].geometry} />
                <mesh material={materials.black} geometry={nodes['Plane.028_11'].geometry} />
            </group>
        </group>
    )
}

function Effects() {
    const { gl, scene, camera, size } = useThree()
    const occlusionRenderTarget = useMemo(() => new THREE.WebGLRenderTarget(), [])
    const occlusionComposer = useRef()
    const composer = useRef()

    useEffect(() => {
        occlusionComposer.current.setSize(size.width, size.height)
        composer.current.setSize(size.width, size.height)
    }, [size])

    useFrame(() => {
        camera.layers.set(OCCLUSION_LAYER)
        occlusionComposer.current.render()
        camera.layers.set(DEFAULT_LAYER)
        composer.current.render()
    }, 1)

    return (
        <>
            <mesh layers={OCCLUSION_LAYER} position={[0, 4.5, -10]}>
                <sphereBufferGeometry attach="geometry" args={[5, 32, 32]} />
                <meshBasicMaterial attach="material" />
            </mesh>
            <effectComposer ref={occlusionComposer} args={[gl, occlusionRenderTarget]} renderToScreen={false}>
                <renderPass attachArray="passes" args={[scene, camera]} />
                <shaderPass attachArray="passes" args={[VolumetricLightShader]} needsSwap={false} />
            </effectComposer>
            <effectComposer ref={composer} args={[gl]}>
                <renderPass attachArray="passes" args={[scene, camera]} />
                <shaderPass attachArray="passes" args={[AdditiveBlendingShader]} uniforms-tAdd-value={occlusionRenderTarget.texture} />
                <shaderPass attachArray="passes" args={[FXAAShader]} uniforms-resolution-value={[1 / size.width, 1 / size.height]} renderToScreen />
            </effectComposer>
        </>
    )
}

function App() {
    return (
        <Canvas
            shadowMap
            style={{ background: '#171717' }}
            camera={{ position: [0, 0, 8], fov: 50 }}
            gl={{ antialias: false }}
            onCreated={({ gl }) => {
                gl.toneMapping = THREE.Uncharted2ToneMapping
                gl.outputEncoding = THREE.sRGBEncoding
            }}>
            <ambientLight intensity={0.5} />
            <pointLight position={[0, 60, -100]} intensity={20} />
            <pointLight position={[-50, 0, -50]} intensity={2} />
            <spotLight castShadow intensity={8} angle={Math.PI / 10} position={[10, 10, 10]} shadow-mapSize-width={2048} shadow-mapSize-height={2048} />
            <mesh position={[0, 4.5, -10]}>
                <sphereBufferGeometry attach="geometry" args={[4.9, 32, 32]} />
                <meshBasicMaterial attach="material" transparent opacity={0.5} />
            </mesh>
            <Suspense fallback={null}>
                <Elf />
                <Elf layer={OCCLUSION_LAYER} />
            </Suspense>
            <Effects />
        </Canvas>
    )
}

render(<App />, document.querySelector('#root'))
